node.text: I’m definitely not a healthcare professional but I’d love to share with you the words and practices I try when I’m feeling my most anxious. Thank you @_hi_anxiety_ for including me in this. **Thank you for watching. YES, YOU! and I hope you know that regardless of what internal or external battle you’re fighting right now, you’re never alone. May God continue to bless you and your families. I am wishing you and yours light, love, laughter, peace, perfect health, and endless prosperity. ♥️

node.text:
Do you have questions about the 2020 Census? Join me as I chat with Ximena Alvarez, Media Specialist, U.S. Census Bureau to go over why it is important to take action and participate in the Census. 
Respond to the census here: 2020census.gov #censo2020 #weallgrow #sponsored

node.title: Why it’s important to take action in the Census!

node.text: Happy Birthday 🖤 to one of the biggest loves of my life! @iambrettgray you’re a legend in the making and I am in contestant awe of you as an artist and as a human. Your talent is only outweighed by your compassion and I miss you like crazy. Hope today is the best damn birthday of your life and make sure you take a shot 🥃 for me tonight! (( scroll to reveal our true friendship haha )) 🤍 JJ!!!
